Welcome to your move-in ready POOL home in the highly sought-after Country Place neighborhood in the Steinbrenner High School District! This updated 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom PLUS den pool home is ready for you to move in and start living the Florida lifestyle! The living area boasts a welcoming ambiance and offers direct access to the stunning outdoor oasis with serene views of your yard and water views. The heart of the home, the kitchen, has been updated with granite countertops and ample cabinet space. The highlight of this property is undoubtedly the backyard. Step outside to your private tropical paradise, where you'll find a crystal-clear pool perfect for cooling off on those warm Florida days. The fully screened turf lanai is ideal for entertaining, lounging, or enjoying outdoor dining during these gorgeous autumn evenings. The master bedroom is a spacious retreat with an en-suite bathroom and a walk-in closet and walk-in shower. Two additional bedrooms are perfect for family or guests and share a beautifully appointed second bathroom. Additional features of this home include a 2-car garage, a separate laundry room, and plenty of storage space. The Country Place neighborhood features two community parks! The ROOF was replaced in 2019 and the A/C is brand new in Oct 2023!
